    "NPC","Shopkeeper","Vendor","Trainer","Quest","Shinigami_Guard",
    "SoulReaper","Merchant","Captain","Lieutenant","Guide","Soul",
    "Urahara","Yoruichi","Ichigo","Rukia","Renji","Byakuya",
